X Platform - Admin Dashboard System Documentation

Project Overview

The Admin Dashboard is the central management system of X Platform.

It was designed to provide administrators with full control over the educational platform through a scalable, modular, and production-oriented architecture.

The dashboard allows administrators to manage:

